  "InternalReferences": "10.1109\/TVCG.2006.120;10.1109\/TVCG.2006.147;10.1109\/TVCG.2012.245;10.1109\/VAST.2009.5332628;10.1109\/TVCG.2008.155;10.1109\/TVCG.2012.189",
  "AuthorKeywords": "Visual Ambiguity, Visualization, Node-link diagram, Graph layout, Graph visualization",
