  "InternalReferences": "10.1109\/TVCG.2013.157;10.1109\/TVCG.2011.255;10.1109\/VAST.2010.5652392;10.1109\/VISUAL.1990.146402;10.1109\/TVCG.2009.153;10.1109\/TVCG.2012.279;10.1109\/TVCG.2014.2346419;10.1109\/TVCG.2013.153;10.1109\/TVCG.2009.127;10.1109\/VISUAL.1994.346302;10.1109\/TVCG.2007.70589;10.1109\/INFVIS.2004.60;10.1109\/INFVIS.1995.528686",
  "AuthorKeywords": "Information visualization, interactivity, dimensionality reduction, multidimensional scaling",
