  "InternalReferences": "10.1109\/TVCG.2012.251;10.1109\/TVCG.2013.234;10.1109\/TVCG.2012.220;10.1109\/TVCG.2013.134;10.1109\/TVCG.2007.70541;10.1109\/TVCG.2014.2352953;10.1109\/TVCG.2014.2346320",
  "AuthorKeywords": "Data physicalization, physical visualization, psychophysics, experiment, physical variable",
