  "AuthorAffiliation": "University of Arizona;University of Arizona;University of Arizona",
  "InternalReferences": "10.1109\/TVCG.2011.186;10.1109\/TVCG.2013.184;10.1109\/TVCG.2009.122;10.1109\/TVCG.2014.2346248;10.1109\/TVCG.2010.210",
