  "AuthorAffiliation": "Post Doc in the Department of Statistics, Iowa State University;Member of the faculty in the Human Computer Interaction program, Statistics at Iowa State University",
  "InternalReferences": "10.1109\/TVCG.2012.230;10.1109\/TVCG.2014.2346320;10.1109\/TVCG.2010.161",
